data.description: Welcome to country living! Set on nearly 5 acres, this 4-bedrm, 2-bath home offers an inviting open floor plan, perfect for family gatherings and entertaining. The vast property provides ample room for your horses, and there's even a chicken coop, ready for your feathered friends. A perfect blend of modern comforts with the rustic countryside, making it the idyllic location for your dream homestead. Enjoy rural serenity just minutes from city amenities like stores, restaurants and schools.
